com.tmobile.opensource.casquatch.annotation

Annotation Type CasquatchSpring


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Import(value=CasquatchSpringBeans.class)
 @Documented
public @interface CasquatchSpring
    Triggers Spring code generation. This should be placed on the main Application class
